==Useful Info==
'''Demonspawn black suns''' are demonspawn necromancers found in the [[Pandemonium]]. Black suns are the only demonspawn who can [[see invisible]].

{{monster spells}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], demonspawns with the black sun class could have any base (monstrous, gelid, infernal, or torturous), instead of all of them being gelid.
*Prior to [[0.19]], they could cast [[Malign Offering]].
*Black suns were added in [[0.14]].

[[Category:Demonspawn]]
